            <note xml:id="foot.f2"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2357.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Joseph Dalton Hooker</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD referred to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1218.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Emma Darwin’s</ref> note in his <ref target="./DCP-LETT-4389.xml" resp="#automat">letter to J. D. Hooker of [10 and 12 January 1864]</ref>.</note>
